UC25 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC26 ..> UC2 : <<include>>

' To mention a user, you must send a message first
UC9 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
UC9 ..> UC6 : <<include>>

' To react to a message, you must see/send a message first
UC10 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
UC10 ..> UC6 : <<include>>

' To create a channel, you must join it first (or be auto-added)
UC7 ..> UC8 : <<include>>

' To assign a task, you must create it first
UC22 ..> UC21 : <<include>>

' To view Kanban board, you must have a project first
UC23 ..> UC20 : <<include>>

' ============================================
' EXTEND RELATIONS (Optional - May happen)
' ============================================
' Reset Password extends Login (when user forgets password)
UC4 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>

' Share Screen extends Video Call (optional feature during call)
UC14 ..> UC13 : <<extend>>

' Schedule Meeting extends Video Call (optional way to start)
UC15 ..> UC13 : <<extend>>

@enduml
